                  Winner of the <strong className="text-[#121c2c]">CBSE Cluster XI Kho-Kho Tournament (2019-2020)</strong>. Competing at a national-level tournament instills extreme team loyalty, operational execution speed, physical stamina, and rapid adaptive reflexes under tight timelines.
